{"tid":1427860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"福建幫企圖亂港令我諗到一個有可能令中國陷入內亂危機嘅可能性...！！","createTime":"2019-08-07T08:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:23:14.000Z","uid":213747,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"091ddd1bea59913ef0a00e61fbb24f094fdddf83","tid":1427860,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:06:41.000Z","msg":"黎緊8月8號同11號有傳福建幫號召咗好多鄉親喺福建落黎香港<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我真係好驚佢地亂咁斬會傷及啲廣州/廈門/成都etc.鄉下嘅香港街坊</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果都時真係出意外 <br />\n求吓各位真係千祈唔好去微博叫佢地去福建有仇報仇<br />\n千祈唔好喺啲鄉親wechat group鬧福建人借機斬其他省份嘅同胞</span></strong></span><br />\n仇恨只會愈滾愈大 <br />\n中國大亂就會搞到香港政府同警察都亂架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">p.s.記得唔好用啲太簡單嘅tag例如 #廣州 #重慶 搞到人地到時咩tag都禁哂<br />\n<br />\n仲有我知琴日明明根本冇黑衫去北角 <br />\n但啲親戚group都亂傳話黑衫匿埋咗喺邊度搞事<br />\n各位11號絕對唔好有樣學樣啊 中國會大亂架</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b0e82e1db855aeefde4692c0b88241c3ea2f5aec","tid":1427860,"uid":213747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:08:25.000Z","msg":"好驚香港令中國開始各個省份互片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f4af5513ba94873f0558da7403d514c41a4513","tid":1427860,"uid":213747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"中國已經全力阻止緊依樣野發生架喇<br />\n各位唔好令佢變成現實啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8db2a17cf30424fb5e05c831546af3012c8f18","tid":1427860,"uid":213747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:13:20.000Z","msg":"中國人政府就唔敢反抗<br />\n但省份互片 人民鬥人民會點冇人知<br />\n唔好分化佢地啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaaecb115ca04e24ea16aca0ffab039ee9b7b661","tid":1427860,"uid":213747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:16:46.000Z","msg":"好似太多紅色大字好難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa01ad5535bc8642534ced3b7f760b9757900a3","tid":1427860,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7124ff72c5ccde27f8ef0dcf23440a358cde9a36","tid":1427860,"uid":273670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8b14428773773124adfb24b44b814d711b7351","tid":1427860,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4feb5a86d06cd14652251457135ded07485b3d6f","tid":1427860,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:24:09.000Z","msg":"來源?"},{"pid":"aa4dfc60c036263a7e5b7f1177a778c3b9281fbf","tid":1427860,"uid":213747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"和理非話唔夠膽講光復香港時代革命<br />\n咁11號搞完分化之後再下一個禮拜遊行轉嗌口號<br />\n嗌吓福建獨立 廣州獨立 上海獨立 千錯萬錯都係北京錯<br />\n咁樣會唔會令中國更加危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac99a0b5e2804df08cfb9319a4c5ce57b177fe9","tid":1427860,"uid":278261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:26:38.000Z","msg":"香港潮州人多"},{"pid":"539a060e44a3f3503d9da6df65282fef957b51f4","tid":1427860,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4feb5a86d06cd14652251457135ded07485b3d6f","tid"